                </FooterDetails>
                <Header/>
                <Paragraph>In 2008 and 2009, FDIC agents were active seizing failed banks.  To learn about the process of a bank seizure and the efforts made by the FDIC to shield employees and depositors from the ill effects of a failure, watch the CBS 60 Minutes video "Your Bank Has Failed."</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
